<subSubSection id="1CDF5F80FFB7FFED6DC2FA44FCCFAD2F" pageId="19" pageNumber="1532" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="547A0C0BFFB7FFED6DC2FA44FCCFAD2F" blockId="19.[178,1085,1497,1581]" pageId="19" pageNumber="1532">
Diagnosis: The members of 
<taxonomicName id="93C57788FFB7FFED6F31FA47FD09AEED" authorityName="OPITZ" authorityYear="2015" box="[577,668,1498,1519]" class="Insecta" family="Cleridae" genus="Isoforma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="1555" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="66B1D019FFB7FFED6F31FA47FD09AEED" box="[577,668,1498,1519]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="1532">Isoforma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are distinguishable from superficially similar specimens of 
<taxonomicName id="93C57788FFB7FFED6CE2FA65FD93AD0F" authorityName="OPITZ" authorityYear="2015" box="[402,518,1528,1549]" class="Insecta" family="Cleridae" genus="Artoadenus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="1555" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="66B1D019FFB7FFED6CE2FA65FD93AD0F" box="[402,518,1528,1549]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="1532">Artoadenus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by the shape of the terminal palpomeres; in 
<taxonomicName id="93C57788FFB7FFED6E92FA65FBA8AD0F" authorityName="OPITZ" authorityYear="2015" box="[994,1085,1528,1549]" class="Insecta" family="Cleridae" genus="Isoforma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="1555" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="66B1D019FFB7FFED6E92FA65FBA8AD0F" box="[994,1085,1528,1549]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="1532">Isoforma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
they are securiform whereas in 
<taxonomicName id="93C57788FFB7FFED6C80F98AFDF1AD2E" authorityName="OPITZ" authorityYear="2015" box="[496,612,1559,1580]" class="Insecta" family="Cleridae" genus="Artoadenus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="1555" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="66B1D019FFB7FFED6C80F98AFDF1AD2E" box="[496,612,1559,1580]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="1532">Artoadenus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
they are subsecuriform.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
